x10.matrix.dist

Class DupDenseMatrix

  • x10.matrix.Matrix
    • x10.matrix.dist.DupDenseMatrix

  • public class DupDenseMatrix
extends Matrix
    Implementation of duplicated dense matrix. All duplicated dense matrices are stored in DistArray. Distribution of dense matrices is unique, and one duplication maps to one place.
